### Create a court
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/courts
Authorization: Basic admin yourpassword
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pickleball Court 1",
  "type": "Pickleball",
  "operatingHoursStart": "08:00:00",
  "operatingHoursEnd": "20:00:00",
  "maxDaysOut": 7
}

### Get all courts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/courts
Authorization: Basic admin yourpassword

### Generate slots for the court (replace COURT_ID with the id from your POST response)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/courts/58b2853c-5ade-44a7-b410-0c3a9cfcb77c/generate-slots
Authorization: Basic admin yourpassword

### Get slots for the court
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courts/4715fa53-d5a8-4103-ae9c-308ee77d9a05/slots?startDate=2026-04-14&endDate=2026-04-21

### Reserve a slot (replace SLOT_ID with any id from the slots response)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courts/4715fa53-d5a8-4103-ae9c-308ee77d9a05/slots/2e91eabc-5f44-4d8d-9c67-7e9d4f7f38d6/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookerName": "John",
  "bookerEmail": "thejohnnysavoy@gmail.com"
}
